nagdom.pl - Report Nagios status to Pingdom

DESCRIPTION

Do you have Nagios monitoring your servers? But who is monitoring your Nagios
server?

This script provides a status report readable by Pingdom regarding your
Nagios install.

INSTALLATION

You will need to install POE::Component::Client::NRPE Perl module via CPAN:

$> cpan POE::Component::Client::NRPE

Check to make sure the script is working properly from the command line:

$> chmod 755 nadgom.pl
$> NAGIOS_HOST=localhost ./nagdom.pl

Configure your web server to display the nagios.pl results. A sample config
is included.

Create a Pindom account, and setup monitoring.
